It looks like you are trying to rescale already rescaled images. If the input images have pixel values between 0 and 1, set `do_rescale=False` to avoid rescaling them again.

It looks like you are trying to rescale already rescaled images. If the input images have pixel values between 0 and 1, set `do_rescale=False` to avoid rescaling them again.
